    "body": "### Describe the bug\n\n`resize -1` leads to abort() if options `cmdheight=0 redrawdebug=invalid` are set.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim --clean\r\nset cmdheight=0 redrawdebug=invalid\r\nresize -1\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nresize works\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nnvim is terminated by abort(3).\r\n\r\nabort() is called at line 427 in ui_compositor.c.\r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/8fbe75b3dda7ab3b9e6df0d5406539bde4c80887/src/nvim/ui_compositor.c#L425-L428\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.9.0-dev-877+g228684d2f-dirty\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nUbuntu-22.04, macOS (Mojave etc.)\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\ngnometerminal, Apple's Termial.app\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nbuild from source",
